Update: Hmm well apparently my game doesn't crash when I reach space it was just a coincidence it happened twice in a row, my game is just unstable and crashes about every ~30 mins. If someone could check out my logs and my mods and share their ideas that would be cool.

Update 2: It seems to freeze after slowing down my time warp in space usually. When I check my task manager it says the process is suspended, I'm not sure it that's that Windows 10 just calls processes that aren't responding or if that has something to do with my freezes.
